-y_{2} & \lambda-\frac{8}{3} & -y_{1}\\
-y_{1} & -y_{2} & \lambda-\frac{8}{3}
\end{pmatrix}\\
&=(\lambda-\frac{8}{3})^{3}-3y_{1}y_{2}(\lambda-\frac{8}{3})-y_{1}^{3}-y_{2}^{3}\\
